Classes in org.ejml.alg.dense.linsol used by org.ejml.alg.dense.linsol
LinearSolver
           Computes solutions for systems that have the form:
A*X = B.
where A ∈ ℜ m × n, X ∈ ℜ n × p, B ∈ ℜ m × p, and m ≥ n.
